# AIGrok

AIGrok is an advanced document analysis tool that uses AI to process, analyze, and extract information from documents.

## Features

- üìÑ Process multiple document formats (PDF, TXT, etc.)
- ü§ñ Advanced AI-powered analysis
- üîç Smart content extraction
- üíæ Result caching for performance
- üõ†Ô∏è Extensible plugin system
- üìä Comprehensive reporting

## Quick Start

1. Install AIGrok:

   ```bash
   pip install aigrok
   ```

2. Set up your configuration:

   ```bash
   aigrok config init
   ```

3. Process a document:

   ```bash
   aigrok process document.pdf
   ```

